<div id="Idea_4103"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4103-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4103">Water shortage? Use technology to turn salt water into drinking water. Be Pro-active not Re-active.&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8499-4049">engi0001</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
