<a href="/akira/dtd/4093-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4093">Voter Qualification &nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/9588-4049">Robert Barrett</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Conflicts of interest prevent Judges and Lawyers from working on cases where they have a personal interest. Conflicts of Interest prevent many parties from entering into business arrangements, etc. <br/><br/>Voters should be pre-qualified by employment and income sources electronically, and in the case of conflict of interest, disqualified from voting for particular initiatives or candidates with whom they have a conflict of interest.</div>
